    <title>Arch安装教程（UEFI）</title>
    <link href="/posts/8f757abb/"/>
    <url>/posts/8f757abb/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Arch是什么"><a href="#Arch是什么" class="headerlink" title="Arch是什么:"></a>Arch是什么:</h2><p><em>Arch Linux（或Arch &#x2F;ˈɑːrtʃ&#x2F;)）是一款基于 x86-64 架构的 Linux 发行版。系统主要由自由和开源软体组成，支持社区参与。系统设计以KISS原则（Keep It Simple and Silly,保持简单和愚蠢）为总体指导原则，注重代码正确、优雅和极简主义，期待用户能够愿意去理解系统的操作。 Arch Linux 系统安装、删除和更新软体的软体包管理器叫做 Pacman</em></p><hr><h3 id="ArchLinux的优势"><a href="#ArchLinux的优势" class="headerlink" title="ArchLinux的优势"></a>ArchLinux的优势</h3><ol><li>AUR(ArchLinux User Repo)中完善的社区软件包  </li><li>对于中国大陆用户友好的ArchLinux CN源  </li><li>滚动更新发行版，没有跨版本更新失败的苦恼  </li><li>基本上完全自定义，想要什么就自己安装什么，并没有其他发行版安装一堆自己不需要的东西的苦恼  </li><li>虽然是命令行安装，但是也算是较为友好且直观了，并且没有安装向导就不会出现Debian安装向导那种莫名其妙的报错</li></ol><hr><h3 id="ArchLinux的问题"><a href="#ArchLinux的问题" class="headerlink" title="ArchLinux的问题"></a>ArchLinux的问题</h3><ol><li>滚动更新发行版较为不稳定（虽然还是比隔壁Windows稳定）（除非你有十足的把握，请不要将其用于服务器）  </li><li>AUR内的软件包有很大一部分引用了GitHub内的资源，导致对于中国大陆并不是很友善  </li><li>滚动更新时对于nVIDIA显卡驱动的处理很容易出错，导致无法正常进入系统</li></ol><hr><h2 id="接下来就是正式安装"><a href="#接下来就是正式安装" class="headerlink" title="接下来就是正式安装"></a>接下来就是正式安装</h2><ul><li>接下来的内容全程都是在Live-CD的root账户或chroot环境的root账户下进行的，您并不需要注意当前用户</li></ul><ol><li><p>下载安装盘 这里推荐使用国内镜像站 (<a href="https://mirrors.bfsu.edu.cn/archlinux/iso">https://mirrors.bfsu.edu.cn/archlinux/iso</a>) 建议选择最新版本进行安装</p></li><li><p>刻录安装盘至U盘<br> 网络上关于如何刻录启动盘的教程很多，不进行赘述<br> 推荐Rufus</p></li><li><p>从U盘启动，引导加载器这里我们选择第一个<br> <img src="http://gchat.qpic.cn/gchatpic_new/0/0-0-7F5F6E304EB8FA43586B7E510AA62D44/0" alt="Grub"></p></li><li><p>连接到网络  </p><ul><li><p>确保系统已经启用了网络接口，用<code>ip-link</code>检查：  </p> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ip <span class="hljs-built_in">link</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>要连接到网络：  </p><ul><li>有线以太网 —— 连接网线  </li><li><h2 id="WiFi-——-使用iwctl验证无线网络-首先进入iwctl的交互式界面"><a href="#WiFi-——-使用iwctl验证无线网络-首先进入iwctl的交互式界面" class="headerlink" title="WiFi —— 使用iwctl验证无线网络  - 首先进入iwctl的交互式界面  "></a>WiFi —— 使用<code>iwctl</code>验证无线网络<br>  - 首先进入<code>iwctl</code>的交互式界面  </h2>  <figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autohotkey">            iwctl  <br>            ```  <br>            <br>            - 列出可用的无线网卡  <br>            ```  <br>            [iwd]# device list  <br>            ```  <br>            <br>            - 扫描可用网络（_**注意：这个指令并不会有任何输出，请不要怀疑是网卡亦或是驱动问题**_）  <br>            ```  <br>            [iwd]# station &lt;device&gt; scan （在&lt;device&gt;处填入你所选择的无线网卡）  <br>            ```  <br>            <br>            - 列出可用网络  <br>            ```  <br>            [iwd]# station &lt;device&gt; get-networks  <br>            ```  <br>            <br>            - 连接到网络  <br>            ```  <br>            [iwd]# station &lt;device&gt; connect &lt;SSID&gt; （&lt;SSID&gt;处填入网络名称）  <br>            ```  <br>            <br>            _**提示：```iwctl```支持```Tab```自动补全。你可以不用列出可用无线网卡，而是输入```station ```之后按两次```Tab```来列出可用设备，输入设备首字符后按 ```Tab```进行补全。同理，虽然仍需要```station &lt;device&gt; scan```，但是你可以不需要```station &lt;device&gt; get-networks```，而是在```station &lt;device&gt; connect ```后按两次```Tab```列出可用SSID，输入SSID前几个字符之后按```Tab```补全**_<br><br>    - 使用```ping```验证网络连接<br>    ```  <br>    ping www.baidu.com  <br>    ```  <br>    <br><br><span class="hljs-title">    ![网络](http:</span>//oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/public-cli/free/<span class="hljs-number">4</span>d94ed41af9f32b693e3961de55692af1673113058.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">5</span>. 网络同步时间  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul><p> timedatectl set-ntp true<br> <figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gherkin"><br>6. 建立硬盘分区(这里使用cfdisk演示)  <br>    - 对于现代Linux而言，必要的分区实际上只有根分区（/），还有EFI系统上的EFI分区（本篇不讨论Legacy系统）  <br>    - 不过别的分区也是有存在的意义的，比如交换分区分区，可以让你的系统在RAM爆满的时候不至于彻底卡死，或者是home分区，可以让你在更换发行版的时候无缝衔接  <br>    - 本篇所采用的分区方案是EFI系统分区+根分区+交换分区，并且基于cfdisk做演示  <br>    - 实际上8GB的交换分区是没有必要的  <br><br>    |<span class="hljs-string"> 分区 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 格式 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 大小 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 挂载点 </span>|<br>    |<span class="hljs-string"> :---: </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> :---: </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> :---: </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> :---: </span>|<br>    |<span class="hljs-string"> efi </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> EFI/fat16/fat32 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 512MB </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> /boot/efi或/efi </span>|<br>    |<span class="hljs-string"> swap </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> Linux swap </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 对于RAM高于4GB的设备，推荐4GB&lt;br&gt;对于其他设备，推荐RAM等大swap </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> N/A </span>|<br>    |<span class="hljs-string"> / </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> ext*/zfs/brtfs等&lt;br&gt;这里选择配置最简单的ext4 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> 剩余的全部空间 </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> / </span>|<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> cfdisk<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![分区](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//g</span>chat.qpic.cn<span class="hljs-regexp">/gchatpic_new/</span><span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/0-0-902E7EB8544F74C1F9919365D1587508/</span><span class="hljs-number">0</span>)  <br>    ![分区类型](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">4</span>b68702bb5cbd2b030365beddc95f4ad1673113816.jpg)  <br>    - 用下方<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Type&quot;</span>来选择分区类型  <br><br>    ![选择](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//g</span>chat.qpic.cn<span class="hljs-regexp">/gchatpic_new/</span><span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/0-0-1F91EAB648DAAD17EA2065D2741D59DB/</span><span class="hljs-number">0</span>)  <br>    - 然后选择<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Write&quot;</span>,输入yes，回车  <br><br>    ![写入](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/b14425f365b818afeedfa81a53b63d1d1673114025.jpg)  <br>    - 然后退出  <br><br>    ![退出](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/fedcb99bb0321147db229aea35ec40f31673114120.jpg)  <br><br><span class="hljs-number">7</span>. 格式化分区  <br>    - 查看分区  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> lsblk<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><br><br>![查看分区](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">9</span>c17e0aba462dfeafbaacb2cf35eacac1673114359.jpg)  <br>- 根分区格式化为ext4  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mkfs.ext4 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;root_partition（根分区）<br> <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>efi分区格式化为fat32  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mkfs.fat -F32 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;efi_partition（efi分区）<br> <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>初始化交换分区  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mkswap &#x2F;dev&#x2F;swap_partition（交换空间分区）<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![格式化](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>a2d2310d031a1927013a3169cbc8f9e1673114776.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">8</span>. 挂载分区  <br>    - 根磁盘卷挂载到/mnt  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;root_partition（根分区） &#x2F;mnt<br> <figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino"><br><br>- 用mkdir创建其他剩余挂载点  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mkdir &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;efi<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><br><br>- efi磁盘卷挂载到<span class="hljs-regexp">/mnt/</span>boot/efi<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;efi_partition (efi分区) &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;efi<br> <figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autohotkey"><br><br><span class="hljs-title">![挂载](http:</span>//oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/public-cli/free/<span class="hljs-number">14</span>e850c2633d747cd55e2f8eb17568c21673115182.jpg)<br><br>_**注意： 挂载分区一定要遵循分区挂载点顺序（如先挂载根分区至```/mnt```，再挂载EFI分区至```/mnt/efi```），否则您可能会无法启动系统，或者某些分区不会正常启用。如果创建了swap交换空间卷，使用```swapon```启用它**_<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> swapon &#x2F;dev&#x2F;swap_partition（交换空间分区）<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![swap](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">8</span>f23fba906cc803a761052a473ac5d221673115357.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">9</span>. 安装基本系统<br>    - 更换软件源<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> curl -L -o &#x2F;etc&#x2F;pacman.d&#x2F;mirrorlist “<a href="https://www.archlinux.org/mirrorlist/?country=CN">https://www.archlinux.org/mirrorlist/?country=CN</a>“<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    编辑<span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>pacman.d/mirrorlist，反注释部分链接以提高速度  <br>    ![软件源](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/cafd49b9c3cdcce8d639c630dba5f1841673115566.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">10</span>. 安装必需的软件包<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> pacstrap &#x2F;mnt base linux linux-firmware vim base-devel<br> <figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs xml">    <br><br>    (如果报错记得pacman -Sy archlinux-keyring)  <br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 等待一下哦 这会你可以去泡杯茶～--&gt;</span>  <br>    ~~海記憶體知己，天涯若比鄰，請稍後~~  <br>    ~~正在安装ArchLinux Rolling，坐和放宽~~  <br><br>    ![安装ing](http://oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/public-cli/free/4cb6c37d4a486299a6e13ca06a27f1231673150485.jpg)<br><br>11. 配置fstab  <br>    - 生成fstab  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> genfstab -U &#x2F;mnt &gt;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;etc&#x2F;fstab<br> <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>检查fstab  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> genfstab -U &#x2F;mnt &gt;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;etc&#x2F;fstab<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![配置系统](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/be378a46802bb2e81537b4d27f3c5e1a1673150653.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">12</span>. Change root 到新安装的系统   <br>    ```  <br>    arch-chroot /mnt  <br>    ```  <br>    <br><br><span class="hljs-number">13</span>. 设置时区    <br>    ```  <br>    ln -sf <span class="hljs-regexp">/usr/</span>share<span class="hljs-regexp">/zoneinfo/</span>Asia<span class="hljs-regexp">/Shanghai /</span>etc/localtime <span class="hljs-comment"># hwclock --systohc  </span><br>    ```  <br>    <br><br><span class="hljs-number">13</span>. 本地化  <br>    - 编辑&lt;code&gt;<span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>locale.gen&lt;/code&gt;，然后取消掉 en_US.UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span> UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span> 和zh_CN.UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span> UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span>前的注释（<span class="hljs-comment">#）  </span><br>    ![本地化<span class="hljs-number">1</span>](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">0955</span>e79237167864b1a1082f660694661673150968.jpg)  <br>    ![本地化<span class="hljs-number">2</span>](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">8935</span>bcc11aea3ffad28308f79aa880981673150977.jpg)  <br>    - 然后创建 locale.conf 文件，并编辑设定 LANG 变量&lt;code&gt;echo LANG=en_US.UTF-<span class="hljs-number">8</span> &gt; <span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>locale.conf&lt;/code&gt;  <br>    - _**请不要在这里设置中文locale! &lt;br&gt;因为Linux tty并不包含中文字形，设置中文locale后又会使应用程序显示中文，所以在这里设置中文locale将会导致重启后无法正常显示文字**_<br><br><span class="hljs-number">14</span>. 网络配置  <br>    - 创建&lt;code&gt;hostname&lt;/code&gt;文件  <br>    - 编辑```<span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>hostname```(里面填上自己的主机名)  <br>    ![主机名](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/ec0fa7497a80e0e21061b81bd6f3a3a11673151791.jpg)  <br>    - 添加对应的信息到 ```hosts``` 编辑```<span class="hljs-regexp">/etc/</span>hosts```  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> 127.0.0.1 localhost<br> ::1 localhost<br> 127.0.1.1   设备名.本地名   设备名<br> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-code">    </span><br><span class="hljs-code"></span><br><span class="hljs-code">    ![hosts](http://oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/public-cli/free/478fe8f22208bcf043f200cdfd3380eb1673152281.jpg)</span><br><span class="hljs-code"></span><br><span class="hljs-bullet">15.</span> root密码  <br><span class="hljs-bullet">    -</span> root账户在Linux当中具有极高的权限，甚至高于Windows当中的Administrator（没记错的话是Ring 2）  <br><span class="hljs-bullet">    -</span> 就权当是设置Administrator密码罢了  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> passwd<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![passwd](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/a35fcd6534583b2d5dc16803130e951f1673152463.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">16</span>. 接下来就是安装引导加载程序啦～  <br>    - 目前在Linux上，GRUB绝对属于是最好用且文档最完善的引导加载程序之一，并且配置难度并不高，支持广泛，所以我们在这选择GRUB作为我们的引导加载程序  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> pacman -S dosfstools grub efibootmgr<br> <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>安装grub  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> grub-install –recheck &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda –efi-directory&#x3D;&#x2F;efi<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk"><br><br>![安装grub](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">8215240847</span>b1c4f40117e7bb81ab43161673152633.jpg)  <br>- 还需要生成grub配置文件  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> grub-mkconfig -o &#x2F;boot&#x2F;grub&#x2F;grub.cfg<br> <figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">    <br><br>    ![记录](http:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/public-cli/</span>free/<span class="hljs-number">878</span>eb24464d04a5c387552291efd21651673152755.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">17</span>. 创建普通用户  <br>    - 虽然使用root账户登陆会很爽（指随随便便就能让系统变成一坨没用的数据），但是在root下，很多应用程序会拒绝正常运行，所以我们要创建普通账户  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> useradd -m -G wheel -s &#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash uesrname（用户名可以改成你喜欢的）<br> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-code">    </span><br><span class="hljs-code"></span><br><span class="hljs-bullet">18.</span> 设置用户密码  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> passwd username（同上方用户名）<br> <figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autohotkey">    <br><br><span class="hljs-number">19</span>. 为用户添sudo权限  <br>    - 实际上应该说是为wheel组内的用户添加允许进行sudo提权的操作  <br>    - 使用```visudo```来编辑sudoers文件  <br>        因为visudo会在编辑完成之后查验文件是否正确  <br>    - 反注释```%wheel ALL=(ALL) ALL```  <br><span class="hljs-title">    ![sudoers](http:</span>//oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/public-cli/free/<span class="hljs-number">9621</span>bf1b35276b15974335452c13d4a91673153106.jpg)<br><br><span class="hljs-number">20</span>. 安装DHCP服务  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> pacman -S dhcp dhcpcd<br> <figure class="highlight armasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs armasm"><br><br>- 当然得启用他啦！ 设置开机自启动！(不然就需要重启之后手动分配<span class="hljs-built_in">IP</span>或者手动启动DHCP服务)  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> systemctl enable dhcpcd<br> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-code">    </span><br><span class="hljs-code"></span><br><span class="hljs-bullet">21.</span> 到这里你的Arch就可以启动啦  <br><span class="hljs-bullet">    -</span> 退出chroot环境  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> exit<br> <figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><br><br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>重启  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br> reboot</p><p> &#96;&#96;&#96;</p><ul><li>如果是使用WiFi进行联网的,重启后第一次启动还需要连接WiFi,方法见上文</li></ul></li></ol><hr><p><em><strong>由于还没有安装桌面，所以登陆后还处在命令行模式，桌面等下一期再写吧 咕咕咕</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>作者 <a href="https://github.com/Jackxzj/">Jackxzj</a><br>修复 <a href="https://github.com/ZhaoymOvO/">ZhaoymOvO</a></strong></em></p><p><em><strong>本文在<a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0协议</a>下发表</strong></em></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
